title: A Night in Ireland by Helen O'Hara [FLAC]
description:
A collection of traditional Irish melodies that once heard will stay with you forever. Exquisitely performed on Violin, Harp, Piano and Accordion they capture the essence of the classic Irish melody. With its impromptu concert like atmosphere this recording is a fine introduction to the beauty of Irish music.
